out_desc_tool: A 61-item character recognition list and 150 items adapted from the Hong Kong Test of Specific Learning Difficulties in Reading and Writing (HKT-SpLD  Ho, Chan, Tsang, & Lee, 2000) were combined and administered. The items were arranged in order of increasing difficulty, and the children were required to read each character aloud.
